{"tid":262501,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"2017最靈異女新人：林羨淇","createTime":"2017-05-29T09:43:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T05:02:45.000Z","uid":9428,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8f273ce7697199182780460aef2b0ed0fa6a6a78","tid":262501,"uid":9428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T09:43:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/29/174025_7d9c521a0faeb20da812151007eccebd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F29%2F174025_7d9c521a0faeb20da812151007eccebd.jpg&h=f7b94991&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近日，地鐵出現呢款轟炸式廣告。<br />\n<br />\n呢位貌似「泰臣 X 林夏薇」嘅女新人，個廣告寫住「歌名：男神為我唱首歌；歌手：林羨淇 Suga Lam 」，令市民成頭黑人問號，心入面講咗句：「呢條女做乜9？」，搞到心思思 search 下呢首歌咩料。<br />\n<br />\n首歌可謂近年樂壇最災難歌曲（沒有之一），一入 intro 啲騎呢怪音已令人忍俊不禁，條女把聲接近 99% 由電腦 autotune，仲要 tune 出嚟都係走音，簡直為世界製造電子嘈音。望一望個監製：周啟生！？<br />\n<br />\n可能拍MV前一晚苦練呢首勁舞快歌嘅舞步，以致睡眠不足，MV導演貼心準備關愛座比佢，等佢可以全程帶住副超唔郁，撟腳齋坐，跳都費事，叫幾位 dancers 喺隔離「泣泣樣樣」就算。呢首咁有前瞻性嘅 MV，上載個幾月已經接近27萬 views，更突破地域界限，吸引一班海外樂迷留言讚好，仲勁過「中國Taylor Swift」阿漿。<br />\n<br />\n靈異嘅事情進一步發生。首歌4月推出之後，林羨淇根本無出席過任何公開場合，佢 fanpage 只係出過一個 post，就係 upload 咗張極低清嘅自拍，氣氛靈異，十足「未亡人」:<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/%E6%9E%97%E7%BE%A8%E6%B7%87-Suga-Lam-1672020439769102/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E7%25BE%25A8%25E6%25B7%2587-Suga-Lam-1672020439769102%2F&d=QW2rtRgOdMk2gu85WiT3bwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=6fbbbb2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/%E6%9E%97%E7%BE%A8%E6%B7%87-Suga-Lam-1672020439769102/</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/29/174221_d16daeca78beaf2efb0bbcef210d1a22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F29%2F174221_d16daeca78beaf2efb0bbcef210d1a22.jpg&h=6082b052&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖片來源：網友 Locke Chan 報料）<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kingjerentertainment/photos/a.229707817101090.55175.169934393078433/1512101732195019/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkingjerentertainment%2Fphotos%2Fa.229707817101090.55175.169934393078433%2F1512101732195019%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=QW2rtRgOdMk2gu85WiT3bwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=257f32ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kingjerentertainment/photos/a.229707817101090.55175.169934393078433/1512101732195019/?type=3</a>"},{"pid":"713fc546e79c4397d9f112e0c0f88d4484462017","tid":262501,"uid":9428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T09:45:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/29/174429_05b9b50647ecc95c6e029d80ddf952a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F29%2F174429_05b9b50647ecc95c6e029d80ddf952a6.jpg&h=caa63a51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nFb都搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b2071640ba64cee6e23a2c65b42f2f4ae4aa894","tid":262501,"uid":65582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T09:48:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/29/174429_05b9b50647ecc95c6e029d80ddf952a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F29%2F174429_05b9b50647ecc95c6e029d80ddf952a6.jpg&h=caa63a51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nFb都搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知阿咸琪咸唔咸呢?"},{"pid":"5d535f5275201275fc577c8ed119ae6de3b0747b","tid":262501,"uid":9428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T09:51:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/29/174429_05b9b50647ecc95c6e029d80ddf952a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F29%2F174429_05b9b50647ecc95c6e029d80ddf952a6.jpg&h=caa63a51&s