faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁撚癲 但係廣告去到咁行<br />\n又唔出席活動登台<br />\n係咩玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe6ec10ded980e20e3942da44ddd5ff1b529c5c9","tid":262501,"uid":39049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T10:23:49.000Z","msg":"諗起n 年前有個梁佑嘉..."},{"pid":"18f68f24707cdb377cfa7575d35efa25ae99b637","tid":262501,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T10:24:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"079451d1c47f46f443e7a83b96cf87af75539bfb","tid":262501,"uid":9428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T10:35:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗起n 年前有個梁佑嘉...</blockquote><br />\n好似都有首幾好聽既歌 <br />\n但係呢個真係唔知做乜撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5229a963730653d783d1f0e75abb2df48c6fbc2","tid":262501,"uid":29609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T15:45:08.000Z","msg":"張相有啲似明日花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5404a61cbece810cf2892aa8617270fce0440e9","tid":262501,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T13:06:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V40KH20Hvhw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DV40KH20Hvhw&d=QW2rtRgOdMk2gu85WiT3bwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=b5f50924\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V40KH20Hvhw</a><br />\n第二首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBTW,呢個角度幾好J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i3/MrjCci.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi3%2FMr